quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  8,9,jab tum apne perwar-digaar se faryaad karte they to is ne tumhari dua qubool karli ( aur farmaya ) ke ( tasalii rakho ) hum hazaar firshton se jo aik dosray ke peechay atay jayen ge tumhari madad karen ge
  8,10,aur is madad ko khuda ne mehez basharat banaya tha ke tumahray dil se itminan haasil karen. aur madad to allah hi ki taraf se hai. be shak khuda ghalib hikmat wala hai
  8,11,jab is ne ( tumhari ) taskeen ke liye apni taraf se tumhe neend ( ki chadar ) udha di aur tum par aasman se pani barsaya taakay tum ko is se ( Nehla kar ) pak kar day aur shaytani najasat ko tum se daur kardey. aur is liye bhi ke tumahray dilon ko mazboot kardey aur is se tumahray paon jamaye rakhay
  8,12,jab tumhara perwar-digaar firshton ko irshad farmata tha ke mein tumahray sath hon tum mominon ko tasalii do ke saabit qadam rahen. mein abhi abhi kafiroon ke dilon mein roab وہیبت daaley deta hon to un ke sir maar ( kar ) ura do aur un ka poor poor maar ( kar toar ) do
  8,13,yeh ( saza ) is liye di gayi ke unhon ne khuda aur is ke rasool ki mukhalfat ki. aur jo shakhs khuda aur is ke rasool ki mukhalfat karta hai to khuda bhi sakht azaab dainay wala hai
  8,14,yeh ( maza to yahan ) chako aur yeh ( jaane raho ) ke kafiroon ke liye ( akhirat mein ) dozakh ka azaab ( bhi tayyar ) hai
  8,15,ae ahal imaan jab maidan jung mein kufar se tmhar muqaabla ho to un se peeth nah pherna
  8,16,aur jo shakhs jung ke roz is soorat ke siwa ke larai ke liye kinare kinare chalay ( yani hikmat e amli se dushman ko maaray ) ya apni fouj mein ja milna chahay. un se peeth phairay ga to ( samjhoo ke ) woh khuda ke ghazab mein girftar hogaya aur is ka thikana dozakh hai. aur woh bohat hi buri jagah hai
